# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Accepted residual CVE risks (cannot be remediated upstream from here)
#
#   urllib3 1.26.x   — pip-audit flags CVE-2025-50181, -66418, -66471, -21441,
#                      all fixed only in urllib3 2.x. We're stuck on 1.x because
#                      `elasticsearch7==7.10.1` (which is locked at 7.x for
#                      Wazuh-indexer compatibility) hard-requires `urllib3<2`.
#                      Lifting this requires migrating off elasticsearch7.
#
#   sqlitedict 2.1.0 — pip-audit flags CVE-2024-35515. Upstream has no fix yet
#                      (last release Apr 2024). Pulled in transitively by
#                      ScoutSuite. Either accept or eventually replace ScoutSuite.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

